22:30.440 --> 22:37.088
the number two egg that they were flying. 
different kinds of spray apparatus and so forth on

22:37.844 --> 22:46.894
it. But the other airplane, the number one 
airplane, was not flying. And so, well, if you're

22:55.003 --> 23:04.553
going to have an airplane, you better take a look at 
that thing. And so I went out and again, I had talked

23:07.561 --> 23:30.054
with Mr. Whitmore about this, and I said, you know, 
it may be that we'll have to rebuild that just in

23:07.561 --> 23:30.054
order to get something in the air again to how the 
hell could you go to a potential sponsor and

23:07.561 --> 23:30.054
propose research work if you don't even have an 
airplane with which to do it. And so I'll never

23:30.074 --> 23:34.581
forget the The day we went out there,

